        {
            "title": "登場兩新股表現迥異 傅里葉高收1倍每手賬賺4000元 銅師傅低收逾49%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">今日掛牌的兩隻新股，全日表現各走一方。半導體股傅里葉(03625)升足全日，收報80元，較招股價40元高1倍。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"傅里葉半導體\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/FS-Web2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"傅里葉半導體\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/FS-Web2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">傅里葉半導體</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">以該股1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面賺4000元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">相反，銅師傅(00664)則全程「潛水」，高位42元時仍較招股價60元低30%；收報30.5元，低於招股價49.17%。以1手100股計，認購並獲配每手賬面蝕2920元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15818533-%e7%99%bb%e5%a0%b4%e5%85%a9%e6%96%b0%e8%82%a1%e8%a1%a8%e7%8f%be%e8%bf%a5%e7%95%b0-%e5%82%85%e9%87%8c%e8%91%89%e9%ab%98%e6%94%b61%e5%80%8d%e6%af%8f%e6%89%8b%e8%b3%ac%e8%b3%ba4000%e5%85%83-%e9%8a%85",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/FS-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 16:38:45",
            "source": "bastillepost",
